beer.beer_description: A hazy little Christmas treat from your friends at Garage Project. Brewed with New Zealand grown wheat and malts and nine different hop additions, this big old hazy has more mouthfeel than ya mum's mince pies, all the tropical fruit salad punch of nan's trifle, and just a resinous hint of fresh Christmas tree. This year, to save us from tears, we're giving this IPA to Someone Special (Special)... You. Merry Christmas one and all.
